backend.entity

Class IdsPrice

  • java.lang.Object
    • backend.entity.IdsPrice

  • public class IdsPrice
extends java.lang.Object
    This entity class represents price given by IDS JMK tariff. IdsPrice is given by its value, zone count limit, total time limit in minutes, station limit and variable for indicating zones 100 and 101.
